    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that beauty thing feels like a lie i tell myself to cope. like, what is the point of \"making the most of it\" if the end result is just total oblivion? every achievement, every memory, it all just gets erased eventually. it feels more like we're just running on a treadmill in a dark room. why even bother struggling if the scale of everything just proves we don't matter?",
