      "role": "user",
      "content": "liberation sounds nice in theory but in reality it just feels like being stuck. if everything is going to be erased anyway, then any pain i feel right now is just unnecessary suffering. it feels more logical to just stop fighting the tide sooner rather than later. if there's no objective meaning, why is there this huge pressure to keep dragging ourselves along through all the misery?",
